items.name: Awesome-Swarms-Framework
items.description: A curated list of awesome applications, tools, and resources for the Swarms framework by swarms.ai. Swarms is a powerful, production-grade framework for orchestrating multi-agent AI systems, enabling developers to build everything from simple autonomous agents to complex, collaborative swarms that can solve real-world problems.

items.description: Nashville Hustle A text-based economic simulation game set in Nashville, Tennessee and surrounding areas. Inspired by the classic "Drug Wars" gameplay mechanics, Nashville Hustle puts players in the shoes of an entrepreneur navigating the Music City's economy.

items.name: npc-system-inspector
items.description: Welcome to the NPC System Inspector! This tool is a powerful diagnostic script designed to quickly and efficiently gather comprehensive information about a Windows computer. It collects details on hardware, software, security settings, and system configuration, then compiles everything into a single, professional HTML report.
